select e_page, e_item_id, sum(pv) as pv, count(distinct appsflyer_device_id) as uv
from default.event_pv_hourly
where toDate(time)>='2020-05-01' and toDate(time)<='2020-05-31'
and app_id in ('com.novel.qing.free.bang-bytedance', 'com.novel.jucai.free.bang-bytedance')
and event_date>='2020-05-01' and event_date<='2020-05-31'
and event_name='shushuo_read_total_page'
group by e_page, e_item_id 
order by pv desc
